Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.04,0:00:06.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔阁下  还望您支援斯达尔克与瓦尔林德的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.59,0:00:09.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,巴贝尔阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.21,0:00:13.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合正在跟同盟和谈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不对联合抱希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要您能行动就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.35,0:00:22.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来想必奥赛尔和布鲁塔巴也会脱离同盟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果维拉尔阁下行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.23,0:00:29.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至可以说服父亲让达尔塔尼亚也出兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.65,0:00:32.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下认为米尔扎阁下说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阿尔图克的存亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.32,0:00:38.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要跟联合决裂也应该战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.87,0:00:43.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,由于在君主会议上自己的意见没通过就脱离联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.20,0:00:45.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可是会被世人笑话的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.71,0:00:49.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不想让阿莱克希斯大人伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,害得我方濒临灭亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正是您口中的阿莱克希斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请您不要选择保护名誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.43,0:00:58.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,选择让阿尔图克存活下去的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无法背叛阿莱克希斯大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.02,0:01:08.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子不需要你的意见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟提欧一起回领地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.82,0:01:15.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.53,0:01:23.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧  就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.71,0:01:36.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是感觉那位魔法师的进言是正确的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.59,0:01:40.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,做决定的不是你而是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我奉劝阁下下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该立刻向马丽娜阁下宣誓效忠  归顺于她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.19,0:01:51.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,做决定的是我不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不打算归顺马丽娜・克莱榭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去见证巴贝尔阁下的战斗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.16,0:02:08.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我对瓦尔林德会怎样进攻难关佩内洛普峡谷很感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真不像你的风格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.19,0:03:50.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得只有这样才能拯救阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,假定与同盟的战争不可避免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要看我们怎样防备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想改变战局恐怕很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就只能尽可能地养更多的士兵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我从明天开始在领地巡游吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这回我会让西露卡也随行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:13.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子果然还知去接受我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.41,0:04:41.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似这里的居民有很多都是迪米特里耶的着族嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我打算去布鲁塔巴的国界附近转转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前往下一个村落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.25,0:04:51.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边稍微歇歇脚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好惨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直穿着湿衣服会得病的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最好赶紧换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  柴都湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,冷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的有一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.10,0:06:31.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就不冷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起了在雨中露营的经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.43,0:07:11.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人曾经在各地流浪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.48,0:07:15.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯孤身旅行心里很没底啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:21.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸有提欧大人陪在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说现在很惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我是想让你稍微休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近一直很忙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有君主会议和维拉尔大人的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想着这样或许能让你转换心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就让我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.59,0:07:42.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你现在经常去独角兽城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这让我很不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.84,0:07:48.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心你会不会就此成为维拉尔大人的亲信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.10,0:07:48.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.18,0:07:52.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是提欧大人不惜舍弃爵位也要保护的契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提欧大人还需要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就愿意为您效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉貌似没领会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.37,0:08:13.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是认真为我考虑为我拼命行动对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也想回报你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还想保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,假如哪天维拉尔大人想抢走你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会毫不犹豫地舍弃爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您还从黑魔女的魔法下拯救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会救啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你对我而言很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我想告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:52.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人发现我的感情了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是隐约有所察觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.12,0:08:59.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这可能只是我的一厢情愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这事非常重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我希望能把话说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.26,0:09:12.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人也爱我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说到这个份上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.56,0:09:18.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是魔女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.70,0:09:30.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了我爰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个像影子一样的骑士是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是米尔扎・库切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那人就是达尔塔尼亚的黑太子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻打斯达尔克的城塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就得走沿海的一条没岔路的窄道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是路的东面耸立着岩山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.67,0:11:12.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,南面的海上停着十艘装备有投石器的战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.76,0:11:17.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有情报称 达尔塔尼亚的船团向已贝尔阁下提供了食物与物资
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一直停在近海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.73,0:11:23.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没发用船在在半岛登陆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.77,0:11:27.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成功了也很难击败米尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.57,0:11:31.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上岩山从山脚进攻城塞如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.57,0:11:36.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要爬岩山就不能带马匹和铠甲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,南面这个名叫腐海的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.08,0:11:46.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,时常会涌出可引发混沌灾害的瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.21,0:11:51.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说可以人为让瘴气涌出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.72,0:11:54.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让瘴气涌出有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用风送入贝内洛浦城塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.14,0:12:07.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,守城士兵要么放弃城塞要么就只能等死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  只要趁瘴气消散之时发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多么坚固的城塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必都会轻易陷落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.28,0:12:18.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,利用混沌灾害违反君主道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不堂堂正正的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算获胜了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马妮娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.33,0:12:30.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德不会遭受指责吗  说我们用卑鄙的手段获得了胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不打算当个善良而无能的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕恶名昭影我也要统一大陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然公主殿下有如此觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我等就只管遵守命令去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.98,0:12:49.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我命令你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.44,0:12:52.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,巴贝尔•穆拉德子爵  支持他的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及士兵的投降均不认可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不够彻底的慈悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无异于主动承认我们处于劣势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:13:02.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让世人明白反抗瓦尔林德的人有什么下场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.33,0:13:06.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让布鲁塔巴和奥赛尔那些优柔寡断的君主们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也做出归顺还是死的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拜托你们去办一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能去接触达尔塔尼亚的太子米尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到风向改变的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,湖底无比平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然而时常会动荡会咆哮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,涌动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的毒  甜蜜的毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.68,0:14:05.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,泥泞的毒相互吞噬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毒将化为泡沫化为雾化为霞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.56,0:14:09.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,乘风而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,上涌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:30.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我切身体会刼了瘴气有多残暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.25,0:14:35.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  城塞必定会被无力化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.77,0:14:54.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用布捂着嘴撑到瘴气散去为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,风向早晚会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有米尔扎阁下的协助…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.05,0:16:10.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是人称大陆最强骑士团瓦尔林德的战斗方式吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无非是遵从克莱榭家的教诲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,采取了合理的战斗方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,巴贝尔•穆拉德子爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的圣印归我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说跟预计的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是看了一场好戏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.06,0:16:57.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是瓦尔林德边境伯爵马丽娜•克莱榭的侍女莱拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.90,0:16:58.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同侍女卡密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,找我何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.11,0:17:05.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的主人想见米尔扎阁下一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟的盟主想见我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.59,0:17:28.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯要是知道这场战斗会怎么想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢米尔扎太子怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说是想立刻见面谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  他说只准带马丽娜大人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法与达尔塔尼亚结盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法战胜阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔・康斯坦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有霸王的器量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.71,0:18:05.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无意统一大陆的人已经没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这位便是瓦尔林德边境伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.81,0:18:24.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大工房同盟盟主马丽娜・克莱榭大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.11,0:18:26.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是达尔塔尼亚太子米尔扎•库切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说你为统一大陆想借助我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.45,0:18:31.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲马提亚斯 以及我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都继承了祖父描绘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.08,0:18:41.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,统一大陆 将圣印合为一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果传说正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来混沌的时代也会终结吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说米尔扎阁下也有相同的志向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.35,0:18:57.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你遇上了阿莱克希斯然后坠入了爱河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你得抛弃这份天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有今晚都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你得成为我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.83,0:19:25.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下…下贱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.34,0:19:32.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算跟你睡了我也无法成为你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你把这当成为了今后能够并肩作战的仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还不了解男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就全交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会归顺于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过从现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就成为你的剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.09,0:20:52.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你还走在霸王之道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓会跟你并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.25,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,好计策
